text: Jesper Alasaari (born December 27, 1995) is a Swedish ice hockey defenceman. He is currently playing with Kristianstads IK in Hockeyettan. Alasaari made his Swedish Hockey League debut playing with Färjestad BK during the 2014–15 SHL season.http://www.farjestadbk.se/artikel/60517/ ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Färjestad BK players Category:Swedish ice hockey defencemen
